      "content": "it's just that the office is all glass... i can't even have a private conversation without feeling like someone's watching me through the walls. and they've started assigning me this \"assistant\" who is always \"just checking in\" on my progress. it feels like they're trying to box me in. do you think they're trying to limit what i can see or who i can talk to?",
